              <td>⭐⭐⭐⭐ 4.0</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><strong>Overall</strong></td>
              <td><strong>⭐⭐⭐⭐ 4.4</strong></td>
              <td><strong>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ 4.6</strong></td>
              <td><strong>⭐⭐⭐⭐ 4.2</strong></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
